      <span class="project-hero-tag">// TypeScript · Go · SQL · Web Application</span>
      <h1 class="project-hero-title">Co-op Education Platform</h1>
      <p class="project-hero-subtitle">
        A full-stack cooperative education management system that connects students,
        company supervisors, and university advisors through a unified placement and
        evaluation workflow.
      </p>
